headline: Fresh Step and Ariana Madix Help Singles "Date Cats, Not Humans" This Valentine's Day with First-Ever Bumble Cat Adoption Takeover
summary: This Valentine's Day, Fresh Step and self-professed cat lover Ariana Madix are inspiring singles to skip the drama that comes with dating humans and look for a love connection with an adoptable cat. In this new campaign, "Date Cats, Not Humans," singles are served the perfect solution to their Valentine's Day woes: starting Feb. 3, adoptable cats from leading national animal welfare organization Best Friends Animal Society will take over Bumble in a first-of-its-kind partnership.
